{
  "$schema": "https://yome.work/schema/signature.json",
  "domain": "xl",
  "signature_version": "1.1.0",
  "label": { "zh": "Excel 表格", "en": "Excel Spreadsheet" },
  "helpSummary": "open, new, save, close, books, sheets, sheet, sheet.add, sheet.rename, sheet.delete, sheet.copy, sheet.move, sheet.hide, sheet.protect, sheet.unprotect, sheet.color, get, range, used, find, set, fill, clear, fmt, width, height, row.add, row.delete, row.hide, col.add, col.delete, col.hide, insert, delete, autofill, autofit, sort, filter, filter.clear, freeze, freeze.clear, copy, cut, paste, merge, unmerge, wrap, rotate, indent, group, ungroup, comment, comment.delete, link, name, cf, validation, chart.add, chart.delete, chart.export, image.add, shape.add, pivot.add, pivot.refresh, pivot.field, page, printarea, print, view, zoom, gridlines, headings, recalc, protect.book, props, screen, alerts, undo, export, batch",
  "docs": {
    "zh": "\n## xl 命令 — Excel 表格\n\n### 工作簿\nxl open <文件路径>                    打开 .xlsx/.xls 文件\nxl new [<路径>] [--force]              新建工作簿（给路径则直接落盘）\nxl save [--path=<另存路径>] [--force]  保存（可另存为）\nxl close [--save=true|false]           关闭\nxl books                               列出所有打开的工作簿\n\n### 工作表\nxl sheets                              列出工作表（名称、行、列、是否活动）\nxl sheet <名称>                        切换活动工作表\nxl sheet.add --name=<名称>             新建工作表\nxl sheet.rename <旧名> --name=<新名>   重命名\nxl sheet.delete <名称>                 删除\n\n### 读取\nxl get <单元格> [--format=json|tsv|raw]  读取单元格 (A1, Sheet2@B3)\nxl range <范围>                        读取范围返回 TSV (A1:C10, Sheet2@A1:D100)\nxl used                                返回已用范围 + 行列数\nxl find <关键词> [--in=<范围>]         搜索内容\n\n### 写入\nxl set <单元格> --value=<值> [--type=text|number|auto]  写入值（auto: 数字串按数字写）\nxl set <单元格> --formula=<公式>       写入公式 (如 =SUM(A1:A10))\nxl fill <范围> --values=<TSV>          批量填充（TAB 分列、\\n 分行）\nxl clear <范围>                        清除内容\n\n### 行列\nxl row.add <行号> [--count=1]          在指定行号前插入行\nxl row.delete <行号> [--count=1]       删除指定行\nxl col.add <列号> [--count=1]          在指定列前插入列 (列号: A/B/C...)\nxl col.delete <列号> [--count=1]       删除指定列\nxl width <列号> --size=<宽度>          设置列宽\n\n### 格式\nxl fmt <范围> [--bold] [--italic] [--size=<字号>] [--color=<颜色>] [--bg=<背景色>] [--align=left|center|right] [--numfmt=<格式串>] [--border=<样式>]\n  颜色/背景: 名称(black/red/blue/...) | #RRGGBB | R,G,B\n  numfmt 示例: '0.00' / '0%' / 'yyyy-mm-dd' / '#,##0.00'\n  border: all|top|bottom|left|right|outline （默认 thin 黑色实线）\n  所有参数可任意组合，单个属性失败不影响其他属性\nxl merge <范围>                        合并单元格\nxl unmerge <范围>                      取消合并\n\n### 导出\nxl export --format=pdf|csv --path=<输出路径> [--force]\n\n范围语法: A1 | A1:C10 | Sheet@A1 | Sheet@A1:C10\n路径: ~ 为主目录，相对路径基于 ~/Desktop\n除 open/new/books 外，所有命令作用于当前活动工作簿（需先 open 或 new）\n",
    "en": "\n## xl command — Excel Spreadsheet\n\n### Workbooks\nxl open <file_path>                    Open .xlsx/.xls file\nxl new [<path>] [--force]              Create new workbook (with path: create and save)\nxl save [--path=<save_as_path>] [--force]  Save (or save as)\nxl close [--save=true|false]           Close\nxl books                               List all open workbooks\n\n### Sheets\nxl sheets                              List sheets (name, rows, cols, active)\nxl sheet <name>                        Switch active sheet\nxl sheet.add --name=<name>             Create new sheet\nxl sheet.rename <old_name> --name=<new_name>  Rename\nxl sheet.delete <name>                 Delete\n\n### Read\nxl get <cell> [--format=json|tsv|raw]  Read cell (A1, Sheet2@B3)\nxl range <range>                       Read range as TSV (A1:C10, Sheet2@A1:D100)\nxl used                                Return used range + row/col count\nxl find <keyword> [--in=<range>]       Search content\n\n### Write\nxl set <cell> --value=<value> [--type=text|number|auto]  Write value (auto: numeric string written as number)\nxl set <cell> --formula=<formula>      Write formula (e.g. =SUM(A1:A10))\nxl fill <range> --values=<TSV>         Batch fill (TAB cols, \\n rows)\nxl clear <range>                       Clear contents\n\n### Rows / Columns\nxl row.add <row_index> [--count=1]     Insert rows above row_index\nxl row.delete <row_index> [--count=1]  Delete rows starting at row_index\nxl col.add <column> [--count=1]        Insert columns before column (A/B/C...)\nxl col.delete <column> [--count=1]     Delete columns starting at column\nxl width <column> --size=<width>       Set column width\n\n### Format\nxl fmt <range> [--bold] [--italic] [--size=<font_size>] [--color=<color>] [--bg=<bg_color>] [--align=left|center|right] [--numfmt=<format_string>] [--border=<style>]\n  Colors/bg: name (black/red/blue/...) | #RRGGBB | R,G,B\n  numfmt examples: '0.00' / '0%' / 'yyyy-mm-dd' / '#,##0.00'\n  border: all|top|bottom|left|right|outline (default: thin black solid)\n  All params combine freely; a single attribute failing does not abort others\nxl merge <range>                       Merge cells\nxl unmerge <range>                     Unmerge cells\n\n### Export\nxl export --format=pdf|csv --path=<output_path> [--force]\n\nRange syntax: A1 | A1:C10 | Sheet@A1 | Sheet@A1:C10\nPath: ~ is home directory, relative paths are based on ~/Desktop\nExcept open/new/books, all commands operate on the currently active workbook (open or new first)\n"
  },
  "commands": {
